ballot_measures.title: Amendment 1
ballot_measures.description: Add discharging a firearm in an occupied dwelling or other occupied space and any solicitation, attempt, or conspiracy to commit murder to the list of crimes for which a judge may deny bail

ballot_measures.title: Amendment 2
ballot_measures.description: Prohibit any reduction in a district attorney's compensation during their term in office

ballot_measures.number: Increase Age Limit for Walker County Judge of Probate from 70 to 75 Amendment
ballot_measures.title: Increase Age Limit for Walker County Judge of Probate from 70 to 75 Amendment
ballot_measures.description: Increase the age limit for the judge of probate in Walker County from 70 to 75
